item.title: How To Make A new Home [317]
item.dc:creator: @chocothunda chocothunda
item.description:
@chocothunda wrote:

Okay, well get the coords of you new home, there should be a command like ::mypos, that will give you the coordinations, and add those in all of your teleports, next go to player.java, and search for your old home coords, and replace them with the new ones. That basically makes it so when you make an account, it will spawn at your new home. I hope I explained that well.

Remove that comment you made about retards, some might take it offensively, or make fun of you.
(12 rep isnâ€™t much better.)

Good luck
